    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a reliable workhorse or daily commuter who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical signs of age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and a few permanent stains, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, but it will likely need some routine maintenance, such as new tires and a brake service, in the near future. It's a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
