    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. Mechanically, it performs reliably with a smooth engine and a responsive transmission. The interior is clean and shows only minor signs of use, while the exterior remains in great shape with just a few small scuffs consistent with regular driving. All major features and electronics are fully functional, providing a comfortable and safe driving experience. This car is ready for the road and would make an excellent daily driver or family vehicle.",
