    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving peak, powered by the S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system. Mated to a desirable 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain delivers linear power to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the internal mechanicals are robust, with recent valve adjustments and a refreshed cooling system. This is a purist-spec machine optimized for throttle response and analog feedback.",
